### Create a new user
POST http://localhost:5292/users
Authorization: Bearer mysecrettoken
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Jimmy Cruz",
  "email": "jimmy.cruz22@gmail.com"
}

### Get all users
GET http://localhost:5292/users
Authorization: Bearer mysecrettoken
Content-Type: application/json

### Get a user by ID 
GET http://localhost:5292/users/1
Authorization: Bearer mysecrettoken
Content-Type: application/json

### Update an existing user 
PUT http://localhost:5292/users/1
Authorization: Bearer mysecrettoken
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Luis Doe",
  "email": "luis.doe@example.com"
}

### Delete a user 
DELETE http://localhost:5292/users/4
Authorization: Bearer mysecrettoken

### Search for users by name
GET http://localhost:5292/users/search?name=ru
Authorization: Bearer mysecrettoken
Content-Type: application/json

